data.description: Welcome to 1916 SW E Ave, a fantastic investment property located in Lawton! This property features a charming 2 unit duplex, with each unit offering 2 bedrooms and one well-appointed bathroom! One side of the duplex has been recently updated and showcases a truly adorable living space. The modern updates and delightful design will surely capture the hearts of potential tenants. The flexibility of this property is outstanding- you can choose to rent out both units for maximum rental income, or simply purchase and rent out the other unit to generate additional cash flow. With a market rent of $875.00 per unit, the return on investment is exceptional! Call Listing agent for a private showing today! 24 hour notice required! Tenant occupied. Brianna Chappelle 580.360.9625
